{"tid":270705,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達，鄭松泰係咪失敗靈童？","createTime":"2017-06-04T13:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T10:11:29.000Z","uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2564c6a8e32096dc51472d8df7cbbcde6f142c34","tid":270705,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/212944_991affd23196ad57fde52884593dfec3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F212944_991affd23196ad57fde52884593dfec3.jpg&h=bd75dbc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陶君行，季詩傑，任亮憲，黃台仰及想轉生為靈童不過失敗嘅何志光、楊繼昌都夠膽倒黃毓民台，實牙實齒狙擊佢。<br />\n<br />\n但是黃毓達，鄭松泰對黃毓民近日遭遇不聞不問，而且無膽反目、避免招人口實話係反骨仔，請問各位佢兩個係咪靈童失敗者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c189aaa37cc51abe49cc6a8b8ffe985f401bac2","tid":270705,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/213730_5e0518ce370373f15ee61cf6446efe62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F213730_5e0518ce370373f15ee61cf6446efe62.jpg&h=708671c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/213731_3ff29b45af7369836d19d6be4abed8df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F213731_3ff29b45af7369836d19d6be4abed8df.jpg&h=97122a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十七世達賴爭位咁"},{"pid":"a4ef66d2fe4f1bf481577a1f815e19f0b9f09f7b","tid":270705,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/213730_5e0518ce370373f15ee61cf6446efe62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F213730_5e0518ce370373f15ee61cf6446efe62.jpg&h=708671c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/213731_3ff29b45af7369836d19d6be4abed8df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F213731_3ff29b45af7369836d19d6be4abed8df.jpg&h=97122a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十七世達賴爭位咁</blockquote><br />\n搵人改圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a6924290cb31360b4e5679951b705e01411740","tid":270705,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:18:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/213730_5e0518ce370373f15ee61cf6446efe62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F213730_5e0518ce370373f15ee61cf6446efe62.jpg&h=708671c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/213731_3ff29b45af7369836d19d6be4abed8df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F213731_3ff29b45af7369836d19d6be4abed8df.jpg&h=97122a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十七世達賴爭位咁</blockquote><br />\n搵人改圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記錯，係大寶法王先岩"},{"pid":"a21ff8941bcbfb08408094d7494a9cb6d0e1d8d0","tid":270705,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tbsn.org/chinese3/news.php?cid=26&amp;csid=6&amp;id=812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftbsn.org%2Fchinese3%2Fnews.php%3Fcid%3D26%26csid%3D6%26id%3D812&d=DKvAiAsYFaNpUWw8J7SPi8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=0dccfd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tbsn.org/chinese3/news.php?cid=26&amp;csid=6&amp;id=812</a><br />\n<br />\n泰耶多傑與烏金赤列<br />\n我與十七世大寶法王「泰耶多傑」會面之後，延伸出一個問題，這問題是個大謎題。<br />\n　　<br />\n僧人問：「盧師尊面見『泰耶多傑』，那泰耶多傑是真的大寶法王了，另一位『烏金赤列』就是假的了？」<br />\n　　<br />\n我答：「十六世大寶法王圓寂於美國芝加哥，後大體運回鍚金隆德寺荼毘（火化），那時，四大法王子鬧分裂。夏瑪仁波切尋找靈童，認定『泰耶多傑』靈童是十六世噶瑪巴的轉世。大鍚杜仁波切認定『烏金赤列』是十六世大寶法王噶瑪巴的轉世。於是十七世大寶法王，出現了雙胞胎，也就是兩個十七世大寶法王。」<br />\n　　<br />\n這件事，在印度鬧得沸沸揚揚。<br />\n　　<br />\n有人說：「烏金赤列，才是真的。」<br />\n　　<br />\n有人說：「泰耶多傑，才是真的。」<br />\n　　<br />\n兩個大寶法王，困擾藏密白教的傳承，到了十七世竟然出現兩位。<br />\n　　<br />\n當烏金赤列出場，另一派人馬大聲叫囂。<br />\n　　<br />\n當泰耶多傑出場，另一派人馬也同樣叫囂。<br />\n　　<br />\n互相鬥爭。<br />\n　　<br />\n如火如荼。<br />\n　　<br />\n鬧得不可開交。<br />\n　　<br />\n有喇嘛告訴我：<br />\n　　<br />\n「修護法，就知道誰真誰假了！」<br />\n　　<br />\n有藏人告訴我：<br />\n　　<br />\n「我們不管誰真誰假，我們認為兩個都是。」<br />\n　　<br />\n有很多人說：「問一問盧師尊就知道了，他的屈指神算第一靈驗。」<br />\n　　<br />\n我哈哈大笑。<br />\n　　<br />\n僧人問：「誰真誰假？」<br />\n　　<br />\n我答：「以觀音為名，有聖觀音、準提觀音、千手觀音、如意輪觀音、十一面觀音、馬頭觀音、不空罥索觀音、青頸觀音、葉衣觀音、白衣觀音等等等等，你說，那一尊才是真？」<br />\n　　<br />\n我答：「阿彌陀佛有千百億化身，南無三十六萬億，一十一萬，九千五百同名同號阿彌陀佛，試問三十六萬億，一十一萬，九千五百個阿彌陀佛，那一尊才是真？」<br />\n　　<br />\n我答：「轉世的大白蓮花童子有好幾個，試問，那一個是真？」<br />\n　　<br />\n我答：「轉世是不可思議的，蓮華生大士是釋迦牟尼佛、阿彌陀佛、觀世音菩薩的三身合一，試問，蓮華生到底是誰？」<br />\n　　<br />\n我說：「在佛法是可以的，是不可思、不可議的，在同一時代，同時有很多的化身存在，同樣在度化眾生。」<br />\n　　<br />\n僧人聽至此，說：「明白，明白。」<br />\n　　<br />\n我是一名悟者，世俗人那能知也。<br />\n　　<br />\n我講幾句開悟語吧！<br />\n　　<br />\n「真，無有真！」<br />\n　　<br />\n「觀世音菩薩，亦是假名，度眾生也。」<br />\n　　<br />\n「有大寶法王噶瑪巴嗎？」<br />\n　　<br />\n「你是誰？我是誰？大寶法王是誰？眾生是阿誰？阿誰是眾生？」（參）"},{"pid":"a345f1b1b0760f2205ad16f28d816d530aa44d5e","tid":270705,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"CK算唔算靈童"},{"pid":"70f653333dd01d14eeddfbf29ef1def63a92146e","tid":270705,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CK算唔算靈童</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢做過myradio一個耶教節目啫<br />\n俾錢去過黃毓炆區議員培訓課程(馮檢基做導師呢下先好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能因為係毓炆多年fd子)<br />\n黃毓炆淨係喺耶教節目phone in畀 ck同埋蒸魚安<br />\n交流僅限兩三次左右<br />\n普羅fans係要附會無計"},{"pid":"1b60d97cdf6bf3f89d217ba2d61a4b3ff822c4a3","tid":270705,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201